    <string name="tinker_instructions"><![CDATA[Welcome to the Smart Mirror App!\n\n
The Smart Mirror App is the fastest and easiest way to configure and play with your Smart Mirror.\n\n
You can access the basic input/output functions of the Smart Mirror without writing a line of code.\n\n
Tap any pin to get started, select a pin function and tinker with the value. Hold a pin to reset its function. Start with pin D7 - select digitalWrite - blink the attached LED.\n\n
For more information visit: adnandzebic.com/\n\n
Enjoy!]]></string>
